EasyBuild

```json
{
  "application": "EasyBuild",
  "software_requirements": [
    "Python 3",
    "EasyBuild framework",
    "EasyBlocks",
    "EasyConfigs",
    "Apptainer or Singularity (optional for containerized testing)"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    "SLURM cluster with at least 1 node",
    "4 CPU cores per node",
    "At least 100 hours of walltime",
    "Access to the /project/boegelbot file system",
    "Access to /project/maintainers file system",
    "Access to Intel licensing server"
  ],
  "environment_variables": [
    "TOPDIR",
    "CONTAINER_BIND_PATHS",
    "EB_PREFIX",
    "PYTHONPATH",
    "PATH",
    "CPU_ARCH",
    "EASYBUILD_PREFIX",
    "EASYBUILD_BUILDPATH",
    "EASYBUILD_SOURCEPATH",
    "EASYBUILD_GITHUB_USER",
    "EB_PYTHON",
    "EASYBUILD_ACCEPT_EULA_FOR",
    "EASYBUILD_HOOKS",
    "EASYBUILD_CUDA_COMPUTE_CAPABILITIES",
    "PSM3_DEVICES",
    "I_MPI_FABRICS",
    "INTEL_LICENSE_FILE",
    "repo_pr_arg",
    "EB_CMD",
    "CONTAINER_EXEC_CMD"
  ]
}
```
